    tmp = wp.sin((0.59 / v1))
    v0 = wp.cos(v1)
    tmp = 0.53
    v0 = (0.08 + ((v2 + 0.94 / v2 + 0.62) - (v0 + 0.36 / v2 + 0.63)))
    v2 = 0.17
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.15) * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.97) - (v2 + 0.64 / v0 + 0.61)))
